      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive mechanical baseline, including a high-pressure VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement for structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission remains crisp, paired with a variable M Differential Lock that ensures optimal torque distribution. With zero deferred maintenance and an immaculate undercarriage, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and kinematic precision. A true collector-grade chassis for the purist seeking unadulterated longitudinal and lateral performance.",
